<h2>What {{ breed.name }}s Need from Their Food</h2>

<p>{{ breed.name }}s are a {{ breed.sizeCategory }} breed weighing {{ breed.weightRange }}, with a lifespan of {{ breed.lifespan }}. They have a {{ breed.activityLevel }} activity level, which shapes their nutritional needs:</p>

<ul>
